    49 Italian Antipasto Pasta Salad — short pasta with salami/prosciutto, mozzarella or provolone, roasted peppers, olives, artichokes, and Italian vinaigrette.
    50 Pasta Puttanesca Salad — cooled pasta tossed with a puttanesca mix: tomatoes, olives, capers, anchovy, garlic, and parsley.
    51 Caprese Pasta Salad — pasta with cherry tomatoes, fresh mozzarella, basil, balsamic glaze, and olive oil.
    52 Roasted Vegetable Pasta Salad — pasta with roasted zucchini, peppers, eggplant, mushrooms and a garlicky vinaigrette or romesco.
    53 Smoked Salmon Pasta Salad — cold pasta with smoked salmon, dill, capers, red onion, and light crème fraîche or yogurt dressing.
    54 Southwestern Pasta Salad — pasta with black beans, corn, bell peppers, cilantro, avocado, and a lime chipotle or cumin vinaigrette.
    55 Cajun Style Pasta Salad — pasta with smoked sausage or chicken, bell pepper, corn, and a spicy Creole style dressing.
    56 Pasta Salad with Burrata and Heirloom Tomatoes — simple high quality ingredients: pasta, ripe tomatoes, creamy burrata, basil, olive oil.
    57 Mexican Street Corn + Grain Salad (corn + quinoa/barley) — grilled corn with cilantro, lime, cheese mixed into a grain base.
    58 Farro Salad — chewy ancient grain salad with roasted vegetables, herbs, lemon, and shaved cheese.
    59 Taco Salad (protein mix) — greens or shells topped with seasoned beef, shredded chicken, beans, cheese, and salsa
    60 Chef's Salad — mixed greens with sliced turkey, ham, hard boiled egg, cheese, and seasonal veggies.
    61 Ambrosia Salad — citrus segments, pineapple, marshmallows, coconut, and whipped cream or yogurt.
    62 Tropical Fruit Salad — mango, pineapple, papaya, and banana with lime, chili, or coconut.
    63 Mango and Avocado Salad — sweet mango with creamy avocado, lime, cilantro, and chili flakes.
    64 Jellied Fruit Salad (classic retro style) — fruit set in gelatin, sometimes with marshmallows or nuts.
    65 Spiced Fruit Chaat (Indian fruit salad) — mixed fruit with chaat masala, lemon, and sometimes toasted seeds.
    66 Kisir (turkish salad)


